After watching this show, complaint about low class contents of TV shows than movies are removed. This Marvel show is some how is equal to a blockbuster Hollywood movie. Charlie Cox is marvelous in his Daredevil role, all the episodes from 1 to 13 compel to see the Charlie. The other promising acting shown by John Bernthal as Frank Castle/Punisher brings the life in show, which brings the excitement to show the actions of punisher again and again. This Netflix show brings us, to return back to the TV. Those persons have some complaints about the Low contents of TV shows, must see one time, all doubts will be removed.